{"article_id":"ioJUhNLPeWGROCVW","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Trump administration is considering an order","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"to block the entry of migrants at the southern border","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"using the same authority as its earlier travel ban ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"a person familiar with the matter said ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"as thousands of Central Americans make their way toward the U.S .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"The action ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"if implemented ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"would effectively bar those","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"seeking asylum","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"from entering the country .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"President Donald Trump is weighing a range of possible options","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"designed to prevent undocumented migrants from crossing the U.S.-Mexican frontier ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"according to a White House official familiar with the discussions .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"Both people spoke on condition of anonymity","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"as no final decision has been made .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"The travel ban ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"announced shortly after Trump took office ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"affected people from seven countries , five of them with Muslim majorities .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"The executive order","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"being looked at now","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"would deny asylum claims","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"based on national security concerns","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"and would give broad authority to officials at the border ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"the person said .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"The New York Times reported on Thursday night","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"that the administration was considering an order","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"that would bar migrants ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"including those","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"requesting asylum ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"who try to enter the country from Mexico ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"a significant escalation of presidential power on immigration policy .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"The White House official wouldn ' t confirm the Times report and others ,","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"that several legal , executive and legislative remedies were on the table .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Trump has repeatedly sought to underscore undocumented immigration as an issue before the midterm congressional elections on Nov. 6 ,","depth":4},{"id":35,"text":"and he has blamed Democrats for the so-called caravan of Central American migrants","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"that is headed toward the border .","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"\" Every time you see a Caravan , or people illegally coming ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"or attempting to come ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"into our Country illegally ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"think of and blame the Democrats","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"for not giving us the votes","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"to change our pathetic Immigration Laws ! \"","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"he said on Twitter .","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"He claimed","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"that Middle Eastern terrorists are among the the thousands of people","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"traveling from Honduras ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"but later said","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"that there was no evidence","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"to support that assertion .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"The Trump administration plans to send at least 800 additional troops to the U.S.-Mexico border ,","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"according to a third person familiar with the deliberations .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"The president has also threatened to cut off U.S. aid to three Central American countries ; Guatemala , Honduras and El Salvador over the migrants","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"heading from Central America toward the U.S. border .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"The Times article ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"citing anonymous sources ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"that details of the possible executive order were still the planning stages","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"and that whatever emerged was sure to be met with legal challenges .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"In June , a sharply divided Supreme Court upheld Trump ' s ban on travel from the seven countries .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"The restrictions indefinitely bar more than 150 million people from entering the U.S .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"The troops","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"that Trump is sending to the border","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"would join 2,100 National Guard troops","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"who were previously deployed","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"to perform support duties for Department of Homeland Security personnel .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Trump said on Twitter on Thursday","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"that he was \" bringing out the military for this National Emergency \"","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"and promised","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"immigrants","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"unlawfully crossing the border","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"\" will be stopped ! \"","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Cutting aid to the Central American countries is more complicated .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"Much of the money for El Salvador , Guatemala , and Honduras was appropriated by Congress in the form of anti-corruption and good-governance programs .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"Those initiatives have broad support from lawmakers ,","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"who have already promised to put up a fight","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"should Trump try to make good on his threat .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"The migrants began crossing into southern Mexico last Saturday ,","depth":5},{"id":78,"text":"avoiding that country ' s migration authorities and federal police","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"by jumping off the border bridge","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"crossing the Suchiate river","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"or by crossing the river in improvised rafts","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"made of tires and boards ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"according to images from El Financiero Bloomberg TV .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"Under standard U.S. procedures , the migrants ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"assuming","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"they reached the southern border ,","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"would be detained","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"for not having the required documents","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"and asked whether they ' re afraid of returning to their home .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"A person","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"who answers \" no \"","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"would not be admitted into the country .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"A person","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"who expresses fear of persecution or torture","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"would be interviewed by an asylum officer","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"to establish","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"whether there is credible fear of persecution .","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Michael J . Bars , a spokesman for the U.S . Citizenship and Immigration Services , said in an email","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"that the \" extremely low bar \"","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"for establishing credible fear","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"allows economic migrants to abuse the system","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"by posing as asylum seekers ,","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"then disappear before their court dates","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"to live illegally in the U.S .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":209,"left":138,"right":208,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":119,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":114,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"